catherinebot will do the following:

* remind channels of upcoming events based on output from robinbot
* repeat reminders until marked done
* look for emoji reactions to know when a reminder is finished

robinbot will do the following:

* take in an opening night date and show name
* take in a template file with data on relative show dates
* create calendar entries based on opening night and relative dates
* create data file for catherinebot to use as reminder dates

template fields we need:

* relative date (days/months before/after opening)
* title for calendar entry
* reminder text to post on slack
* channel to be notified
* how far ahead of event to notify
* how often to notify until marked complete
* create calendar date? Y/N
* create slack reminder? Y/N
